    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3497dffb9776c6367c9cf93e05d6d277.poster.avif?t=1768660537\" width=640 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3497dffb9776c6367c9cf93e05d6d277.webm?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3497dffb9776c6367c9cf93e05d6d277.mp4?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Far beneath an icy ocean, Maritime Operative Daniel awakens alone aboard his submarine. His mission to revive COLONY 1265—an abandoned deep-sea mining and research facility—takes a deadly turn as reactivated systems unveil fragments of its haunting past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/32aecf7d247a69136aab5aa9e03b0844.poster.avif?t=1768660537\" width=640 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/32aecf7d247a69136aab5aa9e03b0844.webm?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/32aecf7d247a69136aab5aa9e03b0844.mp4?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guided only by VIRGIL, his AI companion, Daniel must navigate seven interconnected facilities scattered across the ocean floor, each step bringing him closer to a chilling truth hidden in the darkness. But some horrors are better left buried - something watches, something waits. Descend into the unknown. Revive the colony. Unearth the truth. And remember - survival is expected.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the depths of the Arctic in this first-person horror game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the deep-sea facilities in your submarine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mystery of why the facilities were abandoned in the first place.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources, and interact with the environment to complete your mission.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid dying from drowning, fire, suffocation, and attacks from monsters and unknown lifeforms.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3c62d760f7db8fc9398bc565be4080f5.poster.avif?t=1768660537\" width=640 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3c62d760f7db8fc9398bc565be4080f5.webm?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/3c62d760f7db8fc9398bc565be4080f5.mp4?t=1768660537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
